olynesia\", \"from\": 3867, \"to\": 3883}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When President Emmanuel Macron of France visited the territory in 2021, he acknowledged that the state owed a \\\"debt\\\" to French Polynesia for the 193 nuclear tests.\", \"from\": 3885, \"to\": 4048, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3900, \"end\": 3915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 3919, \"end\": 3925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999225074164, \"rank\": 7.74920298686891e-08, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the territory\", \"from\": 3934, \"to\": 3947}, {\"ngram\": \"the state\", \"from\": 3978, \"to\": 3987}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"debt\", \"from\": 3993, \"to\": 4000}, {\"ngram\": \"French Polynesia\", \"from\": 4005, \"to\": 4021}, {\"ngram\": \"the 193 nuclear tests\", \"from\": 4026, \"to\": 4047}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We did it here because we said to ourselves: 'It's lost in the middle of the Pacific, it will not have the same consequences,'\\\" Mr. Macron said.\", \"from\": 4050, \"to\": 4195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4183, \"end\": 4189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0278110577002983e-37, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the middle\", \"from\": 4110, \"to\": 4120}, {\"ngram\": \"the Pacific\", \"from\": 4124, \"to\": 4135}, {\"ngram\": \"the same consequences\", \"from\": 4154, \"to\": 4175}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Elsewhere in the Pacific, American nuclear testing devastated atolls in what is now the independent country of the Marshall Islands.\", \"from\": 4197, \"to\": 4329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Pacific\", \"from\": 4210, \"to\": 4221}, {\"ngram\": \"the independent country\", \"from\": 4281, \"to\": 4304}, {\"ngram\": \"the Marshall Islands\", \"from\": 4308, \"to\": 4328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The United Kingdom did the same in places under its sway.\", \"from\": 4330, \"to\": 4387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4334, \"end\": 4348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9976151540276578, \"rank\": 0.0023905470554515117, \"text\": \"United Kingdom\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"places\", \"from\": 4365, \"to\": 4371}, {\"ngram\": \"its sway\", \"from\": 4378, \"to\": 4386}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not just us,\\\" said Heinui Le Caill, a representative at the Polynesian assembly.\", \"from\": 4389, \"to\": 4475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4455, \"end\": 4465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999608917, \"rank\": 3.935470235171057e-11, \"text\": \"Polynesian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just us\", \"from\": 4399, \"to\": 4406}, {\"ngram\": \"Heinui Le Caill\", \"from\": 4414, \"to\": 4429}, {\"ngram\": \"a representative\", \"from\": 4431, \"to\": 4447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Justice is needed across the Pacific.\\\"\", \"from\": 4476, \"to\": 4515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4477, \"end\": 4484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justice\", \"score\": 0.9992917506271941, \"rank\": 0.000708751345409979, \"text\": \"Justice\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justice\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justice\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Pacific\", \"from\": 4502, \"to\": 4513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While government medical researchers have found elevated rates of thyroid cancer in French Polynesia, the local cancer institute, established in 2021, said that overall cancer rates are, in fact, lower than those in metropolitan France, as the mainland is known.\", \"from\": 4517, \"to\": 4779, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4608, \"end\": 4617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.306694662769439e-22, \"text\": \"Polynesia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\"}, {\"begin\": 4733, \"end\": 4752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metropolitan_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"metropolitan France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metropolitan_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metropolitan_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"government medical researchers\", \"from\": 4523, \"to\": 4553}, {\"ngram\": \"elevated rates\", \"from\": 4565, \"to\": 4579}, {\"ngram\": \"thyroid cancer\", \"from\": 4583, \"to\": 4597}, {\"ngram\": \"the local cancer institute\", \"from\": 4619, \"to\": 4645}, {\"ngram\": \"overall cancer rates\", \"from\": 4678, \"to\": 4698}, {\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 4707, \"to\": 4711}, {\"ngram\": \"the mainland\", \"from\": 4757, \"to\": 4769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, many Polynesians contend that the true toll of the weapons testing is undercounted.\", \"from\": 4780, \"to\": 4870, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4792, \"end\": 4803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999436113, \"rank\": 5.609704005772901e-11, \"text\": \"Polynesians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the true toll\", \"from\": 4817, \"to\": 4830}, {\"ngram\": \"the weapons testing\", \"from\": 4834, \"to\": 4853}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because of local taboos, some people die at home without ever going to state health facilities.\", \"from\": 4871, \"to\": 4966, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"local taboos\", \"from\": 4882, \"to\": 4894}, {\"ngram\": \"some people\", \"from\": 4896, \"to\": 4907}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 4915, \"to\": 4919}, {\"ngram\": \"health facilities\", \"from\": 4948, \"to\": 4965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Until recently, many cancer patients were sent overseas for care, meaning that some of their cases were not added to the disease tally, Polynesian legislators said.\", \"from\": 4967, \"to\": 5131, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5103, \"end\": 5113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999608917, \"rank\": 3.935470235171057e-11, \"text\": \"Polynesian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many cancer patients\", \"from\": 4983, \"to\": 5003}, {\"ngram\": \"care\", \"from\": 5027, \"to\": 5031}, {\"ngram\": \"their cases\", \"from\": 5054, \"to\": 5065}, {\"ngram\": \"the disease tally\", \"from\": 5084, \"to\": 5101}]}, {\"sentence\": \"President Moetai Brotherson of French Polynesia said that four of his family members had died of diseases that can be induced by radiation.\", \"from\": 5133, \"to\": 5272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5143, \"end\": 5160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moetai_Brotherson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Moetai Brotherson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moetai_Brotherson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moetai_Brotherson\"}, {\"begin\": 5171, \"end\": 5180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.306694662769439e-22, \"text\": \"Polynesia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his family members\", \"from\": 5199, \"to\": 5217}, {\"ngram\": \"diseases\", \"from\": 5230, \"to\": 5238}, {\"ngram\": \"radiation\", \"from\": 5262, \"to\": 5271}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His grandfather was buried in a coffin lined with lead because of fears that the radioactivity in his body would leach into the soil.\", \"from\": 5273, \"to\": 5406, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His grandfather\", \"from\": 5273, \"to\": 5288}, {\"ngram\": \"a coffin\", \"from\": 5303, \"to\": 5311}, {\"ngram\": \"lead\", \"from\": 5323, \"to\": 5327}, {\"ngram\": \"fears\", \"from\": 5339, \"to\": 5344}, {\"ngram\": \"the radioactivity\", \"from\": 5350, \"to\": 5367}, {\"ngram\": \"his body\", \"from\": 5371, \"to\": 5379}, {\"ngram\": \"the soil\", \"from\": 5397, \"to\": 5405}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last fall, Mr. Brotherson gave a speech at the United Nations pushing for a formal investigation into the damage caused by the nuclear testing and for a peaceful decolonization of the territory.\", \"from\": 5408, \"to\": 5602, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5455, \"end\": 5469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7028703617664842e-23, \"text\": \"United Nations\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mr. Brotherson\", \"from\": 5419, \"to\": 5433}, {\"ngram\": \"a speech\", \"from\": 5439, \"to\": 5447}, {\"ngram\": \"a formal investigation\", \"from\": 5482, \"to\": 5504}, {\"ngram\": \"the damage\", \"from\": 5510, \"to\": 5520}, {\"ngram\": \"the nuclear testing\", \"from\": 5531, \"to\": 5550}, {\"ngram\": \"a peaceful decolonization\", \"from\": 5559, \"to\": 5584}, {\"ngram\": \"the territory\", \"from\": 5588, \"to\": 5601}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ruling Tavini party, which has called for independence from France, was founded in the late 1970s with a singular mission: to urge a halt to nuclear detonations in French Polynesia, known locally as M\\u0101'ohi Nui.\", \"from\": 5603, \"to\": 5817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5667, \"end\": 5673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999225074164, \"rank\": 7.74920298686891e-08, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 5778, \"end\": 5787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.306694662769439e-22, \"text\": \"Polynesia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The ruling Tavini party\", \"from\": 5603, \"to\": 5626}, {\"ngram\": \"independence\", \"from\": 5649, \"to\": 5661}, {\"ngram\": \"the late 1970s\", \"from\": 5690, \"to\": 5704}, {\"ngram\": \"a singular mission\", \"from\": 5710, \"to\": 5728}, {\"ngram\": \"a halt\", \"from\": 5738, \"to\": 5744}, {\"ngram\": \"nuclear detonations\", \"from\": 5748, \"to\": 5767}, {\"ngram\": \"M\\u0101'ohi Nui\", \"from\": 5806, \"to\": 5816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"From a political standpoint, the issue of the nuclear tests has long been superimposed on the quest for independence,\\\" Mr. Brotherson said.\", \"from\": 5819, \"to\": 5959, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a political standpoint\", \"from\": 5825, \"to\": 5847}, {\"ngram\": \"the issue\", \"from\": 5849, \"to\": 5858}, {\"ngram\": \"the nuclear tests\", \"from\": 5862, \"to\": 5879}, {\"ngram\": \"the quest\", \"from\": 5910, \"to\": 5919}, {\"ngram\": \"independence\", \"from\": 5924, \"to\": 5936}, {\"ngram\": \"Mr. Brotherson\", \"from\": 5939, \"to\": 5953}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While the tests may have now stopped, people are still dying as a consequence.\", \"from\": 5960, \"to\": 6039, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tests\", \"from\": 5967, \"to\": 5976}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5999, \"to\": 6005}, {\"ngram\": \"a consequence\", \"from\": 6025, \"to\": 6038}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The French state needs to take responsibility.\\\"\", \"from\": 6040, \"to\": 6087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6044, \"end\": 6050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.9999992127326011, \"rank\": 7.760955941025154e-07, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"responsibility\", \"from\": 6071, \"to\": 6085}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oscar Temaru, who is the founder of the Tavini party and a former president of French Polynesia, led an effort to file at the International Criminal Court a complaint against France for crimes against humanity.\", \"from\": 6089, \"to\": 6299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6089, \"end\": 6101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Temaru\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Oscar Temaru\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Temaru\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Temaru\"}, {\"begin\": 6175, \"end\": 6184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.306694662769439e-22, \"text\": \"Polynesia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polyne